(1) Anti-personnel landmines and specially designed components therefore;




(2) Complete 'MANPAD' systems (with or without missiles, including related launching equipment and rockets) and specially designed components therefore - unless for demonstration to the government, and only in cases where the demonstration will be of a basic nature, involve no live firing and no transfer of sensitive data, and not enhance the recipients capability to operate MANPADS;




(3) Missiles for MANPAD systems (including missiles which can be used without modification in other applications) - unless for demonstration to the government, and only in cases where the demonstration will be of a basic nature, involve no live firing and no transfer of sensitive data, and not enhance the recipients capability to operate MANPADS.




